SMS Template
Builder (2021)
This was my first app back in college. User’s built
messages templates and sent them to other
users across multiple services like SMS,
WhatsApp, discord, skype and others. It featured
text-to-voice via the Google’s Api.

Citizen Science
Social Network
(2022)
Focus was created with Flutter, and it featured
infinite scrolling. Users could create citizen
science projects, download project data, and
contribute to on-going projects. It also featured
a gamified tinder-like function that let users
answer community questions.
